      • TYPE_ACCESSIBILITY_OVERLAY

        public static final int TYPE_ACCESSIBILITY_OVERLAY
        Window type: Windows that are overlaid only by an android.accessibilityservice.AccessibilityService for interception of user interactions without changing the windows an accessibility service can introspect. In particular, an accessibility service can introspect only windows that a sighted user can interact with which they can touch these windows or can type into these windows. For example, if there is a full screen accessibility overlay that is touchable, the windows below it will be introspectable by an accessibility service regardless they are covered by a touchable window.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • TYPE_SPLIT_SCREEN_DIVIDER

        public static final int TYPE_SPLIT_SCREEN_DIVIDER
        Window type: A system window used to divide the screen in split-screen mode. This type of window is present only in split-screen mode.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
